                     <interp inst="t18260914-245-person1361" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I heard an alarm, and saw the prisoner in the passage - he was taken to the watch-house, and this hat was given to me.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260914-245-person1362">
                  GEORGE 
                  TAYLOR
               <interp inst="t18260914-245-person1362" type="surname" value="TAYLOR"></interp>
