                     <interp inst="t18260914-245-person1362" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw the prisoner, and helped to secure him; I saw the hat taken from him; a handkerchief was in it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260914-245-person1363">
                  CHARLES 
                  BRETT
               <interp inst="t18260914-245-person1363" type="surname" value="BRETT"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260914-245-person1363" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18260914-245-person1363" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I went down the alley, and saw the prisoner in a passage with a hat on his head.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I saw the hat in the road; I took it up, and, as it rained, I put it on my head; I took my brother's supper, and was returning - they came and asked me what I had got there - I said a hat which I had found.</p>
